result.title: Uzbekistan subregional contest!
result.content:
Somebody knew which university will take place Uzbekistan subregional contest?

UPD1 Uzbekistan subregional contest will take place in Tashkent on November 13, 2016.

Uzbekistan Subregional Contest in 2016 will take place online. Teams from Uzbekistan universities must take part in it at their universities, under observation of their coaches. To take part, coach must completely register teams at Baylor registration system and send the list of teams to neerc@mail.ifmo.ru before November 10, 2016.

The start of the contest will be at 13-00 Uzbekistan Time (UTC+5).

UPD 2 NEERC 2016 will take place in St. Petersburg, Barnaul, Almaty and Tbilisi on December 3-4, 2016.



UPD 3 All teams, who solved 4 or more problems, except for out-of-concours teams and teams who ranked 5-th and lower in their university, are qualified to Regionals (25 teams total).
